Subject: Re: [T2] Severe Flooding Solved (long)

Ray,

You might consider checking your venting on the gas tank.

If the vent is stopped up, then the expansion of the fuel from a warm 
engine is pressurizing the gas tank.

Just a thought.

Cheers, dave

